{"tid":1556050,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"好多人話皇仁書院係名校 其實佢只係一間訓練奴隸為當權者服務的工廠","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T17:56:21.000Z","uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"02e9f5df12a421eea3d8476c02bdfd29c20c77c3","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"我就1988-1995讀皇仁（唔信自己去時事台fact check，我上過壹週刊）<br />\n成績就屬於差嗰一班<br />\n上堂中意諗無謂嘢<br />\n例如物理老師教緊optics<br />\n我就喺度諗究竟如果真係快過光速係唔係可以實現時光倒流<br />\n上數學堂仲衰<br />\n老師教similar triangle我因為有出去補習學咗congruent triangle，就on99諗100%similar係唔係即係congruent<br />\n本身諗下無罪<br />\n老師們一向知我精神有啲問題<br />\n上堂唔搞事淨係遊魂佢哋都唔會理我<br />\n但我今次賤格到掲咗去congruent triangle個頁睇<br />\n激怒咗偉大及被受尊崇的數學老師陳立蓮<br />\n被佢狂鬧<br />\n亦因浪費了同學們寶貴的上課時間<br />\n所以全班同學都好憎我<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"54b6fd7507db75d6790d4c934fbe7f91d7059abb","tid":1556050,"uid":288071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔只你一間，唔關名唔名校事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71c292cc621add8b36db8be057727c8f360c8f1","tid":1556050,"uid":53374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇劉細良？"},{"pid":"9b479eb6b3b72505d3fdba549e86d379d791ef8a","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:34.000Z","msg":"但我仲仇恨陳老師<br />\n其實陳老師想話俾我聽喺權力面前只能認命認錯<br />\n所以全班同學都好尊敬佢<br />\n因為陳老師嘅價值觀就係香港賴以成功的核心價值<br />\n全班同學勤力讀書都係想做奴隸為當權者服務啫<br />\n不過有一個數學天才就唔多妥佢<br />\n但係佢亦無搞事<br />\n只係每一堂數學堂都瞓覺<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"cf017e0a51e334da6258753564f306a00ee1702b","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54b6fd7507db75d6790d4c934fbe7f91d7059abb","tid":1556050,"uid":288071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔只你一間，唔關名唔名校事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87630d617bbdcbf4656733a27da249726a1c1f8c","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c71c292cc621add8b36db8be057727c8f360c8f1","tid":1556050,"uid":53374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇劉細良？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:56:57.000Z","msg":"會考狀元（2A)、全校第一<br />\n能言善辯<br />\n好像是人類歷史上最叻的人"},{"pid":"51dd9ffbcd7d330fcfe8f6204f07dfe651874868","tid":1556050,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"咁你最後AL咩成績"},{"pid":"bf6f01504815bab0623892e960b10d979b077a0f","tid":1556050,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71c292cc621add8b36db8be057727c8f360c8f1","tid":1556050,"uid":53374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇劉細良？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:13.000Z","msg":"佢係李求恩嫁，都唔關皇仁事，你問黎想做咩？"},{"pid":"4360a511dc387d6293c186dc27c2cf4fbd710259","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"51dd9ffbcd7d330fcfe8f6204f07dfe651874868","tid":1556050,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"咁你最後AL咩成績"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"3A"},{"pid":"9e181f9e24a5bdddefd8062cd0b362df1cf9b665","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf6f01504815bab0623892e960b10d979b077a0f","tid":1556050,"uid":274607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71c292cc621add8b36db8be057727c8f360c8f1","tid":1556050,"uid":53374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇劉細良？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2