ke":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"好記仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"都唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8415425a59a628f1c832787d97d426b1c5fa52d5","tid":1556050,"uid":175032,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"年輕嘅會員留意番<br />\n樓主係有考到A-Level版嘅烏大龜"},{"pid":"fc38f50e67b8d74072685d88d2e8d3bf3170efcb","tid":1556050,"uid":288071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf017e0a51e334da6258753564f306a00ee1702b","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54b6fd7507db75d6790d4c934fbe7f91d7059abb","tid":1556050,"uid":288071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔只你一間，唔關名唔名校事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"好耐之前已經有人將教育用作為出產倒模人嘅工具，上流社會當在奴役工人時少咗人就可以揾個一模一樣嘅人黎替換。咁啱香港醒嘅都走曬去讀神科，邊個時代都係咁，得返D狗屎垃圾出黎做老師，人又蠢又唔想煩，咪用最直接嘅方法，咪姐係兇人記過嗰D逼人就範。蠢嘅人唔知自己蠢，講多都無用。"},{"pid":"f3ad2d02152351c33f4859004882a107920ae2c0","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"講埋數學天才個故事先<br />\n其實我理科同英文真係唔掂，又對中史中國文學有興趣（因為係中文，唔使查字典），想讀文科<br />\n但阿媽迫我讀理科<br />\n勉強揀咗中英數附加數物理化學生物地理經濟嚟讀<br />\n（勁嘅就唔會讀地理而讀電腦）<br />\n咁就同數學天才一齊坐<br />\n我中四中五其實就完全唔知偉大而被受尊敬的陳立蓮上堂教咩<br />\n完全聽唔明<br />\n又因為仇恨佢<br />\n成日諗住日後報仇<br />\n更加唔想聽書<br />\n數學天才就唔知點解堂堂都瞓著<br />\n本來大家相安無事<br />\n不過有一日...<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"88b8c541d97b9fed1c3fcb5c0bb728978e3a4fd3","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8415425a59a628f1c832787d97d426b1c5fa52d5","tid":1556050,"uid":175032,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"年輕嘅會員留意番<br />\n樓主係有考到A-Level版嘅烏大龜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"唔太了解佢"},{"pid":"b52cbd19d5de503375e2b711d7da4993c9b2a2c2","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc38f50e67b8d74072685d88d2e8d3bf3170efcb","tid":1556050,"uid":288071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf017e0a51e334da6258753564f306a00ee1702b","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54b6fd7507db75d6790d4c934fbe7f91d7059abb","tid":1556050,"uid":288071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"唔只你一間，唔關名唔名校事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"好耐之前已經有人將教育用作為出產倒模人嘅工具，上流社會當在奴役工人時少咗人就可以揾個一模一樣嘅人黎替換。咁啱香港醒嘅都走曬去讀神科，邊個時代都係咁，得返D狗屎垃圾出黎做老師，人又蠢又唔想煩，咪用最直接嘅方法，咪姐係兇人記過嗰D逼人就範。蠢嘅人唔知自己蠢，講多都無用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11028fafe6efbfdcfd9f64d23acd5e89d491d19","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:15:35.000Z","msg":"同場加映<br />\n<br />\n我的中學同學謝x中<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544928</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2fdd27439e339549a86b38763914e561931b7651","tid":1556050,"uid":311867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88b8c541d97b9fed1c3fcb5c0bb728978e3a4fd3","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8415425a59a628f1c832787d97d426b1c5fa52d5","tid":1556050,"uid":175032,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"年輕嘅會員留意番<br />\n樓主係有考到A-Level版嘅烏大龜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:14:05.000Z","msg":"唔太了解佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"烏大龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd9039593b4b12f119d05c75202a3b7ee73c7fd","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T15:38:14.000Z","msg":"嗰日偉大而被受全班同學尊崇尊敬尊重的陳立蓮老師表演解一條勁難嘅數學題<br />\n好像是circle搵tangent（其實我真係完全唔識）<br />\n佢用咗成個鐘寫滿成個黑板（用咗100個steps咁啦）<br />\n全班同學都覺得老師係天才<br />\n老師亦流露出自己真係好勁嘅樣（我仇恨佢所以就心諗你揸住教師用書之嘛，又唔係一步步講解）<br />\n可能佢勝利沖昏頭腦<br />\n將佢嗰100個steps擦晒<br />\n然後叫醒數學天才<br />\n吩咐佢出黑板解呢條數學題<br />\n再喝令全班同學唔准出聲<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"a8347e91153ea51eb50fc54995d1ea9041d54d6b","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"咁數學天才咪行出去<br />\n同陳立蓮老師一模一樣咁解（留意番佢係啱啱瞓醒，陳立蓮老師係跟住教師用書）<br />\n但佢解到第80個step（其實無數住嘅，不過方便大家理解，當係80先）<br />\n用咗另一個方法<br />\n佢嘅解法直接去咗陳立蓮老師第85個step(即係本教師用書行咗寃枉路）<br />\n跟住解到尾<br />\n答案同陳立蓮老師一樣<br />\n陳立蓮老師好唔忿氣咁叫佢「返去坐低」<br />\n數學天才於是返埋位繼續瞓<br />\n全班亦唔出聲<br />\n呢件事亦成為學校禁忌<br />\n大家都唔會提起（小息食飯會唔會講呢我就唔知，因為人哋唔歡迎我加入）<br />\n至於陳立蓮老師以後教師弟會繼續跟教師用書定用數學天才嘅方法呢？亦不得而知<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"005599282957c8bfd9d66f806639eac793ad9b95","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"瞓先"},{"pid":"16585e55e745e44c0abcdecad0f0d305f250632e","tid":1556050,"uid":68944,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b271432fe19da394167804a432dbdc93cc3fb5f0","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"（瞓唔著打埋呢段先）<br />\n我會考成績十分差<br />\n無記錯全班尾三四<br />\n雖然都原校升到中六<br />\n但打聽到陳立蓮老師會繼續教中六數學<br />\n唔想入唔到大學同受多兩年罪<br />\n於是就轉去文科<br />\n（用中英數地理經濟五科成績入）<br />\n最後俾我爆冷在A level考到3個A<br />\n加上當年理科班勁人去咗美國讀書<br />\n留低嘅唔知咩事全部失準<br />\n咁就俾我攞埋獎學金<br />\n亦令1993-1994總領䄂生徐紹基仇恨我<br />\n日後要求佢在壹週刊做記者嘅女友（劉細良下屬）害我<br />\n但班師弟唔知我嘅心路歷程<br />\n以為我係走線專家<br />\n聽說後來不少理科師弟用呢招中六轉文科以希望A level考取好成績<br />\n亦有人說有人中三選科刻意選理科不選電腦選地理務求中六入番文科<br />\n最後傳出學校禁止理科生用會考五科報中六文科嘅政策<br />\n正式杜絕走線<br />\n（待續）"},{"pid":"d3baaa3d96fe114b39f62ec2245e72e04ec7ea42","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16585e55e745e44c0abcdecad0f0d305f250632e","tid":1556050,"uid":68944,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"其實我唔識你<br />\n唔好扮熟"},{"pid":"dd037310f0047cb31fc158f29b3e9ed5cddc13cd","tid":1556050,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71c292cc621add8b36db8be057727c8f360c8f1","tid":1556050,"uid":53374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇劉細良？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"㩒錯負皮，sorry"},{"pid":"90e0030b00f2f5596301bf96215d385893de8626","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd037310f0047cb31fc158f29b3e9ed5cddc13cd","tid":1556050,"uid":223244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c71c292cc621add8b36db8be057727c8f360c8f1","tid":1556050,"uid":53374,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"點睇劉細良？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"㩒錯負皮，sorry"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:24:38.000Z","msg":"無所謂啦<br />\n小學生先會在意正負評"},{"pid":"ff0b62ac6ce62e903ff9f5f53b861b21e93a72da","tid":1556050,"uid":43737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"痴線佬post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e660279cf7f044bdc3728a48a7322641d5b459","tid":1556050,"uid":262489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"樓主真係癲佬 話係咁話 我識幾個qc仔都係癲佬 完全唔服學校個套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7aedbdad65a49fb0614fe321c059b48ce10b202","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff0b62ac6ce62e903ff9f5f53b861b21e93a72da","tid":1556050,"uid":43737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:30:44.000Z","msg":"痴線佬post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:24:37.000Z","msg":"唔係"},{"pid":"01a3f6ea3a7f7d86a4e560d50c568de26cec1d9f","tid":1556050,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85e660279cf7f044bdc3728a48a7322641d5b459","tid":1556050,"uid":262489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"樓主真係癲佬 話係咁話 我識幾個qc仔都係癲佬 完全唔服學校個套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:25:02.000Z","msg":"講事實又癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033c7c96e4ac4c39bf67d0a6d6bf263bae69f1cd","tid":1556050,"uid":311867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"16585e55e745e44c0abcdecad0f0d305f250632e","tid":1556050,"uid":68944,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T23:26:57.000Z","msg":"都四十幾歲人啦。。。仲成日講番中學點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj